title: Geth 1.5.0 (Dev) crashing across multiple pools, networks.
body:
Installed 1.5.0 from the dev branch, everything was fine for a few days. 
Since last night, geth keeps crashing on all of my pools with the following output on all three pools.

All are on different hardware, with different network providers.

Resource allocation is not an issue, as all machines have gigs of overhead in both storage and memory.
